data.description: This gorgeous, immaculate west facing ranch home boasts exceptional accessibility features including: zero entry from front, garage & basement, 36” doors, 5’ turning radius, custom chair lift, 2 super poles to aid with bathing, raised handrails + more. The sprawling floorplan flooded natural light at every turn includes: 4 bedrooms, den, Livingroom w/dual fireplace, enormous kitchen w/island, pantry, solid surface counters, higher dishwasher & oven, XL master suite w/dual vanities, jetted tub, zero entry 2 person shower w/dual shower heads, CA closet w/pull down poles. Huge FIN walkout LL w/2 more BR’s, an office or in-law suite boasting exterior door & private 2nd drive. Backyard includes a full PVC privacy fence, sprinkler system, deck & covered patio. 3 car heated garage w/220V, insulated attic.  Updated roof, 2 zone HVAC, humidifier, H2O htr & softener, central vac. Corner lot + Gretna schools. Active neighborhood w/modern playground, pavilion & HOA annual dues include pool access!
